    "Id": "chassisdef_capra_CP-J18",
    "Name": "Capra",
    "Details": "The CP-J18 is a minor but practical refinement of the CP-J16, trading the two Machine Guns and their ammunition for a pair of additional heat sinks. The change addresses the original's biggest weakness, giving pilots more sustained firing capacity when bringing all ten Small Lasers to bear in a close-range engagement. Speed and armor remain identical, keeping the same aggressive closing playstyle intact.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.97</color></b>",
