  "StockRole": "Light Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "Taurus Territorial Industries built this one to prove the Concordat could still produce real BattleMechs, and it does the job. Nothing fancy, just a fast light mech that gets in your face and unloads everything at once. Raiders used to underestimate it constantly, which worked out well for whoever was piloting one. It is not going to win a slugging match against anything heavy, but it was never supposed to.",
